# Zaxa Studio — Design System Rules

## Core Principles

- **Dark only.** The site forces `class="dark"` on `<html>`. Never implement or consider light-mode variants in new work.
- **Minimal and premium.** Prefer restraint over decoration. Every visual choice should feel intentional.
- **Green is an accent, not a base color.** Use `var(--green-400)` / `#1DCD9F` sparingly — for interactive highlights, focus states, key labels, and brand moments. Body text is never green.

---

## Token Files

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `src/styles/tokens.css` | **Single source of truth.** All primitives: color palette, spacing, radius, shadows, typography scale, transitions, z-index. |
| `src/styles/theme.css` | Maps tokens → component semantic variables (`:root` / `.dark`) and exposes them to Tailwind via `@theme inline`. |
| `src/styles/glass.css` | Glassmorphism utility classes, all referencing token variables. |

---

## Color Rules

### IMPORTANT: Never hardcode color values

- NEVER use raw hex (`#1DCD9F`, `#000000`, `#141414`) in component files.
- NEVER use raw `rgba(29, 205, 159, ...)` — use the token variables instead.
- Use CSS custom properties: `var(--green-400)`, `var(--color-border-accent)`, `var(--color-text-secondary)`, etc.
- In Tailwind classes, prefer semantic utilities: `text-foreground`, `bg-background`, `border-border`, `text-muted-foreground`.

### Color Token Reference

```
Background hierarchy (darkest → lightest):
  --color-bg-base           #000000  (page canvas)
  --color-bg-surface        #080808  (slightly elevated)
  --color-bg-surface-raised #141414  (cards, panels)
  --color-bg-surface-overlay#1C1C1C  (modals, dropdowns)

Text hierarchy:
  --color-text-primary      #EDEDED  (main body text)
  --color-text-secondary    #8A8A8A  (supporting / metadata)
  --color-text-tertiary     #525252  (placeholders, disabled)
  --color-text-accent       #1DCD9F  (green accent — use sparingly)
  --color-text-on-accent    #000000  (text on green backgrounds)

Borders:
  --color-border-subtle          rgba(255,255,255, 0.05)
  --color-border-default         rgba(255,255,255, 0.09)
  --color-border-strong          rgba(255,255,255, 0.15)
  --color-border-accent          rgba(29,205,159,  0.25)
  --color-border-accent-strong   rgba(29,205,159,  0.50)

Accent fills (tinted backgrounds):
  --color-accent-fill-xs   rgba(29,205,159, 0.04)
  --color-accent-fill-sm   rgba(29,205,159, 0.08)
  --color-accent-fill-md   rgba(29,205,159, 0.12)
  --color-accent-fill-lg   rgba(29,205,159, 0.18)

Brand greens:
  --green-400  #1DCD9F  (primary)
  --green-500  #169976  (secondary / hover)
  --green-600  #0D7C5E  (pressed / deep)
```

